history.content:
Yes. Fall 2020 enrollment was slightly over half full. Getting into the class should not be a problem, given that you've taken CS 189 (no grade requirement, according to Fa20 TA).

__________

Enrollment for undergrads for 285 actually happens the first week of classes. As far as I know, I think it's impossible to phase 1 it as an undergrad. A form should be released late Summer and all you have to do is fill it out and then course staff will automatically enroll you into 285 (via CalCentral it'll suddenly show up). This is how it worked Fall 2020 (not part of staff/don't know anyone on staff but this is from my personal experience enrolling in it last semester)
